    <PackageTags>sidata;platform;framework;sidata platform;sidata framework;Sistem Loyalti Pelanggan 2;SLIP2;web;api;restful;webapi;</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
      v.2026.06.1
      - first build
      - BARU: endpoint utk Merchant dan Customer

      catatan perubahan lengkap liat disini: &lt;root github&gt;/Sidata/CHANGELOGS.md
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
